Name: planktOs
About the game: Planktos is a beautiful underwater exploration experience. Possess and cleanse a variety of fish that have become corrupted by an unknown evil. Solve challenging puzzles and discover the unique abilities of the marine life. Help the little spirit navigate an enchanting realm and release Elders trapped in crystal prisons. Avoid fearsome predators and traps in your attempt to rescue all of the Elders.
